from datetime import date, timedelta

def find_nth_weekday(year, month, weekday, n):
    # Start from the first day of the month
    current_date = date(year, month, 1)
    
    # Find the first occurrence of the weekday in the month
    while current_date.weekday() != weekday:
        current_date += timedelta(days=1)
    
    # Move to the nth occurrence of the weekday
    nth_weekday_date = current_date + timedelta(weeks=n-1)
    
    # Check if the nth occurrence is within the same month
    if nth_weekday_date.month == month:
        return nth_weekday_date.day
    else:
        return -1

# April 2022, looking for the 3rd Tuesday
year = 2022
month = 4
weekday = 1  # Monday is 0, so Tuesday is 1
